{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":9,"arguments_yes_count":0,"arguments_no_count":1,"id":666,"created_at":"2015-10-16T11:01:15+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-16T11:13:18+0200","body":"<div>Mettre &agrave; disposition des administrations publiques des outils (logiciels, formations, guides)&nbsp;pour leur permettre de&nbsp;<strong>communiquer&nbsp;<\/strong>avec les citoyens \/ consommateurs de mani&egrave;re&nbsp;<strong>simple, compr&eacute;hensible, efficace<\/strong>.&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Si nul n&rsquo;est cens&eacute; ignorer la loi, chacun a le droit de pouvoir la comprendre&nbsp;!<\/p>\r\n<\/div>","versions_count":0,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":1,"author":{"username":"Julie Renahy","displayName":"Julie Renahy","uniqueId":"julierenahy","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/julierenahy","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":97,"title":"Section 4","subtitle":"Information des consommateurs","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[{"isContribuable":false,"id":5393,"body":"La proposition concerne la relation administration - administr\u00e9, or la pr\u00e9sente section concerne le droit des consommateurs.","created_at":"2015-10-17T17:15:06+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-17T17:15:06+0200","is_enabled":true,"votes_count":0,"type":0,"is_trashed":false,"author":{"username":"Tan\u00e9l\u00e9o","displayName":"Tan\u00e9l\u00e9o","uniqueId":"taneleo","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/taneleo","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"_links":{"show":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-4-information-des-consommateurs\/publier-des-informations-comprehensibles-par-tous-1#arg-5393","edit":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-4-information-des-consommateurs\/publier-des-informations-comprehensibles-par-tous-1\/arguments\/5393\/edit","report":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-4-information-des-consommateurs\/publier-des-informations-comprehensibles-par-tous-1\/arguments\/5393\/report"},"has_user_voted":false,"has_user_reported":false}],"modals":[],"votes":[{"user":{"username":"Lucie Laroche","displayName":"Lucie Laroche","uniqueId":"lucielaroche","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/lucielaroche","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Damien Roch","displayName":"Damien Roch","uniqueId":"damienroch","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/damienroch","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Da Vitoria","displayName":"Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Da Vitoria","uniqueId":"fredericdavitoria","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/fredericdavitoria","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Jeanne Varasco","displayName":"Jeanne Varasco","uniqueId":"jeannevarasco","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/139_default_avatar.jpg"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/jeannevarasco","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Tan\u00e9l\u00e9o","displayName":"Tan\u00e9l\u00e9o","uniqueId":"taneleo","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/taneleo","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}}],"appendices":[{"body":"<p>Fournir aux consommateurs&nbsp;une information&nbsp;<strong>facile &agrave; comprendre<\/strong>&nbsp;et&nbsp;<strong>simple &agrave; trouver<\/strong>&nbsp;est fondamental si l&rsquo;on veut <em>vraiment<\/em> simplifier leurs d&eacute;marches, les informer sur leurs droits et&nbsp;leurs obligations, les responsabiliser,&nbsp;r&eacute;duire les co&ucirc;ts qu&#39;engendre la complexit&eacute; des documents qu&#39;on met &agrave; leur disposition...<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quels que soient les outils, quelles que soient les technologies, les efforts pour rendre l&#39;information&nbsp;<strong><em>accessible&nbsp;<\/em><\/strong>et<strong><em>transparente&nbsp;<\/em><\/strong>resteront vains si l&#39;on ne se pr&eacute;occupe pas avant tout&nbsp;de&nbsp;<strong>rendre l&#39;information compr&eacute;hensible.<\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>Notre constat&nbsp;: les efforts sont nombreux et co&ucirc;teux, mais les textes ne sont accessibles et transparents que pour une poign&eacute;e d&#39;initi&eacute;s.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>Les pays anglo-saxons l&#39;ont compris depuis longtemps et r&eacute;digent maintenant en &quot;<strong>Plain Language<\/strong>&quot;, &quot;<strong>Plain English<\/strong>&quot;. &nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quelques uns des nombreux sites &agrave; ce sujet :&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li><a _src=\"http:\/\/www.plainlanguage.gov\/plLaw\/\" class=\"external-link\" href=\"http:\/\/www.plainlanguage.gov\/plLaw\/\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 160, 208); box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">http:\/\/www.plainlanguage.gov\/plLaw\/<\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\r\n\t<li><a _src=\"http:\/\/www.write.co.nz\/Resources\/Plain+English+articles\/Benefits+of+plain+English+for+the+public+sector.html\" class=\"external-link\" href=\"http:\/\/www.write.co.nz\/Resources\/Plain+English+articles\/Benefits+of+plain+English+for+the+public+sector.html\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 160, 208); box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">http:\/\/www.write.co.nz\/Resources\/Plain+English+articles\/Benefits+of+plain+English+for+the+public+sector.html<\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\r\n\t<li><a _src=\"http:\/\/www.plainlanguagenetwork.org\/kimble\/Writing1.pdf\" class=\"external-link\" href=\"http:\/\/www.plainlanguagenetwork.org\/kimble\/Writing1.pdf\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 160, 208); box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">http:\/\/www.plainlanguagenetwork.org\/kimble\/Writing1.pdf<\/a>\r\n\t<ul>\r\n\t\t<li>je vous conseille l&#39;excellent livre de Kimble &quot;Writing for Dollars, Writing to Please: The Case for Plain Language in Business, Government, and Law&quot; (2012)<\/li>\r\n\t<\/ul>\r\n\t<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n<p>A quand le &quot;Plain French&quot; ? Pourquoi ne pas avoir maintenu&nbsp;le logiciel LARA (Logiciel d&#39;Aide &agrave; la R&eacute;daction Administrative)&nbsp;?<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>La start-up&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/www.prolipsia.com\/\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 160, 208); box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" target=\"_blank\">Prolipsia&nbsp;<\/a>se propose&nbsp;aujourd&#39;hui&nbsp;de &nbsp;:<\/p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>sensibiliser &agrave; l&#39;importance de la qualit&eacute; r&eacute;dactionnelle dans les questions de&nbsp;transmission d&#39;information, d&#39;accessibilit&eacute;, de transparence, de partage des donn&eacute;es, etc.<\/li>\r\n\t<li>apporter son expertise aux divers r&eacute;dacteurs<\/li>\r\n\t<li>mettre &agrave; disposition son&nbsp;<strong>logiciel d&#39;analyse de contenu, Captilo<\/strong>, qui d&eacute;tecte ce qui peut &ecirc;tre source de confusion dans un texte et accompagne&nbsp;le r&eacute;dacteur dans la correction.&nbsp;<a _src=\"http:\/\/www.captilo.com\" class=\"external-link\" href=\"http:\/\/www.captilo.com\/\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 160, 208); box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">www.captilo.com<\/a>&nbsp;<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>","type":{"title":"Explication de l'article"}}],"ranking":364,"is_trashed":false,"title":"Publier des informations compr\u00e9hensibles par tous","votes_nok":1,"votes_ok":8,"votes_mitige":0,"_links":{"show":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-4-information-des-consommateurs\/publier-des-informations-comprehensibles-par-tous-1","edit":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-4-information-des-consommateurs\/publier-des-informations-comprehensibles-par-tous-1\/edit","report":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-4-information-des-consommateurs\/publier-des-informations-comprehensibles-par-tous-1\/report","type":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-4-information-des-consommateurs"},"user_vote":null,"has_user_reported":false},"rankingThreshold":null,"opinionTerm":1}